In the MATTER OF the GUARDIANSHIP OF I.P. and K.P., R.G., Petitioner-Appellant,
v.
D.K., Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-0861 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 15, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A grandmother appeals the dismissal of her petitions for guardianship of her two grandchildren. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
